he lowest temperature we measured on the barrel was 250, which is more heat than is needed to curl fine hair. It&#39;s never a good idea to use more heat than necessary when styling since it can cause damage over time."]},"id":"33441675-92d5-4444-91fa-f72fe6a6e22e","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Convenience"},"id":"b9026b82-98d5-4d95-8363-bdc7e7926597","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/CHgmhhn4kVPXtCCrzkLuDZ.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"We can&#39;t overstate how hot the tip of the curling iron&#39;s barrel gets – it gets ridiculously hot. While you would expect any tool with the word &#34;iron&#34; in it to be hot, you don&#39;t expect the point at the top of a curling iron to be hot since almost every model on the market comes with a cool-touch tip. And, it wasn&#39;t a hot-but-still-touchable heat like with its competitors – it was as hot as the barrel itself.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/69521-xtava9.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/CHgmhhn4kVPXtCCrzkLuDZ.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"CHgmhhn4kVPXtCCrzkLuDZ","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/CHgmhhn4kVPXtCCrzkLuDZ.jpg","alt":""},"id":"0e4d5930-da82-468e-9c23-3d1f580595a7","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The hot tip wasn&#39;t the only thing that kept this curling iron’s ease of use score low. A couple of the testers reported the clip was too weak, so their hair fell out of it while rolling. That was just on the 1-inch barrel we used for testing that day, though, and sometimes it just takes a little practice to use a new type of clip. In other tests we did, the clip worked fine.","The multiple barrels the curling iron comes with make it a versatile tool. You can use them to create anything from tight ringlets to loose, beachy waves. Each barrel is easy to click into place. The digital screen and long swiveling cord are also convenient additions."]},"id":"5c588b0b-88d3-466c-94ec-3b64dbc26b0e","type":"te